The '''Adobe Museum of Digital Media''' is a [[virtual museum]] dedicated to digital art,<ref name="nyd">{{cite news|publisher=New York Daily News|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/adobe-museum-digital-media-brings-cutting-edge-technology-masses-24-7-article-1.191487|title=Adobe Museum of Digital Media brings cutting edge technology to the masses|date=October 6, 2010|author=Joanna Molloy|accessdate=May 25, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mutualart.com/OpenArticle/From-the-Archives--Trendsetting-Art-for-/5CCCCE200DE94AF2|publisher=Mutualart.com|title=From the Archives: Trendsetting Art for 2012|date=December 28, 2011|accessdate=May 25, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.zeit.de/digital/internet/2011-04/adobe-museum-netzkunst|publisher=Zeit|title=Netzkunst in digitaler Architektur|author=Julian Doepp|date=April 29, 2011|accessdate=May 25, 2016}}</ref> and also commentary on the relationship between digital media and society.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.artandeducation.net/client/Adobe_Museum/|publisher=Art and Education|title=Adobe Museum of Digital Media|accessdate=May 26, 2016}}</ref> It was created and sponsored as a marketing exercise by [[Adobe Systems]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://rhizome.org/editorial/2011/feb/9/moving-museum-online/|title=Moving the Museum Online|author=Michelle Kasprzak|date=February 9, 2011|publisher=Rhizome|accessdate=May 25, 2016}}</ref>

The museum's first exhibition was a video exhibit by [[Tony Oursler]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702303341904575576593459315512|publisher=Wall Street Journal|title=From Old Masters to the Cartoonish|author=Lance Esplund|date=October 30, 2010|accessdate=May 25, 2016}}</ref> Other artists exhibited have included [[Mariko Mori]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.mynavi.jp/news/2011/12/07/046/&prev=search |title=オンライン美術館「AMDM」、森万里子の最新インスタレーション作品を展示 (Online Museum "AMDM", exhibition of the latest installation work of Mariko Mori) |author=Minako Yoshida |date=2011 |accessdate=May 25, 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924175240/http://news.mynavi.jp/news/2011/12/07/046/ |archivedate=September 24, 2015 }}</ref>

